name: seaborn.objects.Plot
describe: The main class for creating a plot using the seaborn objects API.

name: seaborn.objects.Plot.add
describe: Add a new layer to the plot.

name: seaborn.objects.Plot.scale
describe: Set the scales for the plot variables.

describe: Create a facet grid and subplots for each variable combination.

describe: Specify the organization of the plot components.

describe: Link axes across subplots.

describe: Set the theme for the plot.

describe: Save the plot to a file.

name: seaborn.objects.Plot.show
describe: Render the plot and display it.
